&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/LATAM-SANTIAGO-AMBROSIA-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7928&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/LATAM-SANTIAGO-AMBROSIA-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;LATAM- SANTIAGO- AMBROSIA- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;92&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-LA50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-10474&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-LA50B-2015-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- LA50B- 2015- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;91&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/LATAM-SANTIAGO-AMBROSIA-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;With a passion for cooking since childhood, Chef Carolina Baz&aacute;n Ba&ntilde;ados has worked in top kitchens in Paris, Brazil and Peru. Located in the residential neighborhood of Vitacura, dining at Ambrosia takes place in a comfortable, contemporary dining room. Menus change daily based on season and market. The culmination of Chef Baz&aacute;n&rsquo;s passion, experience and relaxed style has earned her a place on 2015 Latin America&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants at #32. Attire is smart casual&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Ambros&iacute;a by phone at +56-22-217-3075 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:contacto@ambrosia.cl&quot;&gt;contacto@ambrosia.cl&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection at the time of booking to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ambrosia requires that&nbsp;Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection be made with 48 hour advance notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ambrosia&rsquo;s tasting menu changes daily therefore ingredients are sourced per the amount of reservations received. Upon booking, guests must confirm if they would like the 8-course tasting menu or A La Carte&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations for 8 or more people must be booked via telephone, no exceptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

